other_tests.findings: Mild dependent atelectasis bilaterally; normal liver, pancreas, spleen, adrenal glands, kidneys, stomach, small bowel loops, colon, and rectum; appendix measures up to 8 mm without surrounding fat stranding; a 3.6 x 2.6 x 3.5 cm ovoid hyperdense right uterine structure with surrounding halo of hypodensity and thin curvilinear hyperdensities at the periphery likely representing blood vessels; no retroperitoneal or mesenteric lymphadenopathy; no free fluid in the pelvis.
